reviewText: DVD's did not run in DVD Player, had to return items.  Language French and unable to change to English.
This show was amazing before this season. I didn't like the new captain or the more military approach. I wish this came in an English version. 2 stars because Lucas and Jonathon were still awesome
I did not like the French version. I do not speak French nor do I read French and I do not write French. I would have purchased this item in English if I had the chance.
